frameDefinitions: An Agent saves a Patient or an Asset from a Harmful_situation.
In this frame, an Agent engages in personal body care by grooming either a Patient or a Body_part.
This frame refers to clothing and its characteristics,  including anything that people conventionally wear.
This frame describes an Agent's gathering of Individuals (people or entities) into a group, the  Aggregate, defined by relative proximity.
This frame describes food and meal preparation.
frameExamples: Israeli commandos <t>rescued</t> the hostages and left.
Claudia dressed in a dark green cotton <t>DRESS</t> clasped round her slender waist with a broad yellow belt , drank a cup of coffee and opened her neglected post .
The police <t>gathered</t> the suspects into a line-up.
Caitlin <t>baked</t> some cookies from the pre-packaged dough.
listRoleDefinitions: The sentient being who rescues the <fen>Patient</fen> or <fen>Asset</fen> from the <fen>Harmful_situation</fen>.
The living being who is rescued by the <fen>Agent</fen>.
The entity that is judged to be valueable which might be lost or damaged by the <fen>Harmful_situation</fen>.
An event that occurs which could result in injury or harm to the <fen>Patient</fen> or <fen>Asset</fen>.
The time at which the <fen>Agent</fen> rescues the <fen>Patient</fen> or <fen>Asset</fen>.
The location at which the <fen>Agent</fen> rescues the <fen>Patient</fen> or <fen>Asset</fen>.
The agent is the person who does the grooming.
The patient is the person who gets washed.
This is the region of the body that gets groomed.
This role identifies the time when the event occurs.
Where the event takes place.
This role identifes the clothing worn.
This role identifies the aggregate that results from the gathering.  It may be expressed either as an adjunct result phrase or as a direct object of a target verb.
Agent is the person who gathers Individuals.
This role identifies the entities that come together to form an Aggregate.

This role identifies the time when the gathering event occurs, if specified.
The crowd assembled <fex name='Time'>at dawn</fex>.

This role identifies the place where the gathering event occurs.
He <t>assembled</t> the children <fex name='Place'>in the hall</fex>.
The <fen>Cook</fen>  prepares the <fen>Produced_food</fen>.
The <fen>Produced_food</fen> is the result of a <fen>Cook</fen>'s efforts.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the cooking creation occurs.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the cooking creation occurs.
